@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_xxqgws(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.sin(wp.exp(v2 + 0.31)) / (wp.exp(tmp + 0.28) + v0))
    v1 = wp.cos(wp.abs((v1 + 0.94 * v1 + 0.68)))
    v0 = 0.73
    tmp = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.67 - v0 + 0.79)) * ((v0 + 0.27 * v1 + 0.17) / wp.sin(tmp + 0.63)))
    data[tid] = v0
